BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ decimeter} = 10 \text{ centimeters} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$dm1] \text{ decimeters} = ``] [__________]{$cm1} [`` \text{ centimeters} ``]

a. [`` [$cm2] \text{ centimeters} = ``] [__________]{$dm2} [`` \text{ decimeters} ``]

END_PGML


